    "body" : "<pre><code>import java.net.URI;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Below also works for me :</p>\n<pre><code>URI uri = URI.create(&quot;http://stackoverflow.com&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>OR</p>\n<pre><code>URI uri = new URI(&quot;http://stackoverflow.com&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n"
